\subtree{
\title{The Reafferent Loop}
\p{The three trits form a reafferent loop:}

\pre{\startverb
FORM (perception of structure)
     ↓
GAME (action via agency)
     ↓
WITNESS (observation of effect)
     ↓
FORM (updated structure)
\stopverb}

\p{This is the spectral gap constraint in action:}

\ul{
\li{Each step has probability 0.25 of jumping to another trit}
\li{Mixing time of 4 steps ensures all trits are visited}
\li{GF(3) conservation ensures balanced inquiry}
}
}
}